    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the car drives reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While the exterior shows some light wear and minor surface scratches, and the interior has been kept clean with only slight signs of use on the seating, the car remains solid and dependable. You can expect a well-performing vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate major repairs needed.",
